Project: Potato

Made in 3 hours by :

  • Haddle- Assets, Programming
  • Charliegregg314 - Programming

People don't like potatoes anymore!

Its time to change that!

Your goal is to distribute 1,000,000 potatoes to the world so that people like them again!

The game is made with pure JS and you can find the code here

P.S this game takes a long time to complete so if you plan on finishing it, leave it open while you check out other games! (Don't worry, the game will mute itself)
